@BookstoreApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5074

### GET all books (page 1)
GET {{BookstoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### GET categories
GET {{BookstoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/books/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### POST - Add a new book
POST {{BookstoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 0,
  "title": "Test Book",
  "author": "Test Author",
  "publisher": "Test Publisher",
  "isbn": "123-4567890123",
  "classification": "Fiction",
  "category": "Mystery",
  "pageCount": 300,
  "price": 14.99
}

###

### PUT - Update a book (replace 1 with the bookId returned from POST)
PUT {{BookstoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 1,
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "author": "Updated Author",
  "publisher": "Updated Publisher",
  "isbn": "123-4567890123",
  "classification": "Fiction",
  "category": "Mystery",
  "pageCount": 350,
  "price": 19.99
}

###

### DELETE - Delete a book (replace 1 with the bookId to delete)
DELETE {{BookstoreApi_HostAddress}}/api/books/1
